@startuml
title Viaverse Business Onboarding / Verification — Activity Diagram
start
:Owner chooses Operate Business;
:Check account capability and eligibility;
:Create business draft;
:Complete profile\nname/category/about;
:Upload verification docs\noptional/required by region;
:Run verification\nmanual/automated;
if (Approved?) then (yes)
  :Create service catalog;
  :Add branch/service area\nhours/capacity;
  :Select plan/trial\nbilling config;
  :Publish-ready check\nprofile/catalog/billing;
  :Publish to search\nand lead routing;
  :Emit BusinessPublished;
else (no)
  :Request changes or reject;
  :Return to profile/docs fix;
endif
stop

note bottom
Business can be drafted before verification,
but public search visibility and lead routing require publish-ready policy.
end note
@enduml
